1140
1:0:14,403 --> 1:0:18,198
- I beg pardon.
- "I beg pardon." What are you so polite about?


1141
1:0:18,198 --> 1:0:20,367
For the same reason you're not.


1142
1:0:20,367 --> 1:0:24,288
It's the way I was brought up.


1143
1:0:24,288 --> 1:0:26,29
This fighting...


1144
1:0:26,29 --> 1:0:28,417
That's not why we are here, to fight.


1145
1:0:28,417 --> 1:0:31,962
We have a responsibility.


1146
1:0:31,962 --> 1:0:36,633
This, I have always thought,
is a remarkable thing about democracy...


1147
1:0:36,633 --> 1:0:39,72
that we are...


1148
1:0:39,72 --> 1:0:42,389
Uh, what is the word?


1149
1:0:42,389 --> 1:0:45,559
Notified.
That we are notified by mail...


1150
1:0:45,559 --> 1:0:49,98
to come down to this place
to decide on the guilt or innocence...


1151
1:0:49,98 --> 1:0:54,109
of a man we have never heard of before.


1152
1:0:54,109 --> 1:0:59,573
We have nothing to gain or lose
by - by our verdict.


1153
1:0:59,573 --> 1:1:3,994
This is one of the reasons
why we are strong.


1154
1:1:3,994 --> 1:1:8,165
We should not make it a personal thing.


1155
1:1:8,165 --> 1:1:11,43
Thank you.


1156
1:1:11,43 --> 1:1:13,42
If nobody else has an idea,
