1165
1:1:41,698 --> 1:1:43,784
Well, listen. I, uh...


1166
1:1:43,784 --> 1:1:47,37
I was wondering if, uh, maybe...


1167
1:1:47,37 --> 1:1:49,414
maybe we should take another vote.


1168
1:1:49,414 --> 1:1:53,794
Oh, great. Maybe we can follow this one up
with a little dancing and refreshments, huh?


1169
1:1:53,794 --> 1:1:56,38
- Hmm.
- Mr. Foreman?


1170
1:1:56,38 --> 1:2:0,8
Well, that's okay with me.
Anyone doesn't want to vote?


1171
1:2:0,8 --> 1:2:3,303
- Hey, come on. Come on.
- I'm sorry.


1172
1:2:3,303 --> 1:2:6,89
I think we ought to have an open ballot -
call out our votes, you know.


1173
1:2:6,89 --> 1:2:9,184
Let's see who stands where.


1174
1:2:9,184 --> 1:2:14,439
That sounds fair to me.
Anyone object?


1175
1:2:14,439 --> 1:2:18,151
Okay. I'll call off your jury numbers.
One.


1176
1:2:18,151 --> 1:2:21,29
