1190
1:2:57,482 --> 1:2:59,609
Number 11?


1191
1:2:59,609 --> 1:3:1,528
Not guilty.


1192
1:3:1,528 --> 1:3:3,947
Number 12?


1193
1:3:3,947 --> 1:3:6,366
Number 12.


